text: Ilfete Kryeziu (born 18 October 1998) is a Kosovar footballer who plays as a goalkeeper and has appeared for the Kosovo women's national team. ==Career== Kryeziu has been capped for the Kosovo national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Kosovan women's footballers Category:Kosovo women's international footballers Category:Women's association football goalkeepers
